messages.content: [P/J] mala, im really sorry, but i dont know when ill be back home. got called in by the council.
[P/J] i really have no idea whats gonna happen. i love you, talk to you soon
[M/N] i know you probably wont see this right away but
[M/N] i didnt give you space. i shouldnt have been so aggressive
[P/J] you werent aggressive. i was. im sorry
[M/N] if you need time to think i can stop bothering you
[P/J] why didnt you leave at the lake?
[M/N] i didnt want you to have to be alone
[P/J] i had asked you to leave... i *needed* to be alone
[M/N] i can go if you want
[P/J] id like that. but answer the question first
[P/J] mala i cant do this. im so sorry i want to see you again
[P/J] it just. hurts. in a way that i never thought id feel again
[P/J] call me when you get on please. ill answer no matter what
[P/J] its just really bad right now. i
[M/N] do you want me to come over
[P/J] i dunno. please dont be mad though i know im being hypocritical im sorry
[P/J] sure just. i wanna talk to you. whether i get to see you or not
[M/N] do you want to call while im on my way?
[M/N] whoever you are i know you have polaris' phone
[M/N] where the fuck did you go
[M/N] whoever you are i think you still have polaris' phone
[M/N] what are you doing with him
[M/N] polaris please tell me youre okay
[M/N] where are you? what was that shit with the gravity?
[M/N] polaris last time I saw you you were getting accosted by slime shit
[P/J] you dont have to. im fine
[M/N] have you considered i want to see you
[M/N] jesus fuck polaris were in life or death situations every goddamn day
[M/N] i need to know for certain you arent fatally wounded because i know you wont fucking tell me if you are
[P/J] want me to send a picture
[M/N] yeah but im still coming over
*He sends a poorly taken picture of himself with a pokerface, tongue sticking out, and a peace sign. Uni and Gemi are in the background.*
[M/N] ...do you not want me to come over
[M/N] almost there see you in a sec
[M/N] hey when are you planning on being back here do you want me to head to the house
[P/J] ill be back in a second
[P/J] im heading home. shales place or ours?
[M/N] news came from shale, i think they have your mom
[M/N] not sure if they told you about it so i decided to make it known
[M/N] there was a raid on the plasma zone
[P/J] malachite i just got back from the plasma zone. this is a cruel fucking prank
[M/N] why the fuck would i joke about this
[P/J] this lady is fucking lying. why would my mom be here all of a sudden? morise sent her. or something.
[M/N] we should wait for some sort of confirmation, its very convenient timing
[M/N] if its a trap its one meant for you
[M/N] come home and we can make plans
[P/J] malachite if shes actually a threat i need to go there now
[P/J] time planning could be time shes attacking
[M/N] you have a fucking history of being held hostage at this point dont be a dickhead about this
[P/J] i wont let her take me hostage. ill grab everyone there and warp home
[P/J] well. uh. kinda. lets just say sure
((Polaris calling it a shock bracelet makes me laugh for some reason))
[M/N] im so fucking sorry polaris were getting you out of there
[P/J] its fine. morise hasnt hurt my mom too much for some reason, mostly me
[M/N] what did they do to you
[P/J] i mean of course im thankful for that.. im just kinda suspicious
[P/J] look i want you focusing on getting me and my mom out not if im hurt or not
[M/N] we need to know so we can extract you safely you arent helping anyone by dodging the question
[M/N] we need a plan that will allow for your injuries
[M/N] were getting you out of there i swear
[P/J] using star to type right now. my arms are basically mutilated and my right hand is crushed
[P/J] somnus got a med kit so im bandaged up right now
[M/N] im going to kill morise next time I see them
[M/N] somnus is the good one right
[P/J] mhm. had to leave though. i think she pissed off morise somehow
[M/N] were working on a plan to get you the hell out of there i promise were coming
[M/N] you said you had a shock collar or something hows that work
[P/J] almost got my bracelet smashed off. morise didnt fix it yet, gonna try to get it off before they do
[P/J] whenever i warp out of the plasma zone it shocks me till im out
[M/N] maybe we can get someone in there who knows about that kind of thing
[P/J] ill just have star yank it off
[M/N] thats dumb your arm is broken
[M/N] and how would you get it off of seiko
[P/J] same thing with her i guess
[M/N] morise wouldnt make it that easy
[M/N] theres gotta be some kind of security measures
[M/N] be careful with trying to escape if morise is pissed that might make it more difficult to get you out
[P/J] im gonna yank mine off, get hers off, and then get us the hell out of here
[P/J] if morise catches me before i can get hers off im warping her to you guys. she's gonna pass out from the shock so just find a way to get it off before she wakes up
[M/N] thats fucking stupid why not just warp to us and let us get them off while youre knoked out
[P/J] because morise will just come for us again and we'll be fucking knocked out
[P/J] if i get it off before then we'll have an advantage. if not then at least one of us will be with you
[M/N] if you fuck up they might kill you or cut your hands off or something
[P/J] ill just have sarcio heal me or something
[M/N] he cant heal you if he doesn't have the missing parts
[P/J] well have fucking helio give me the parts then
[M/N] warp to us, well remove the bracelets and heal you before using another plasma to teleport to a safer location
[M/N] itll be fast and morise wont see it coming
[P/J] malachite i cant do it now at least
[P/J] i dont have any feeling in my fucking hands. ill at least need to wait till i have that
[M/N] dont try to take off the fucking bracelets
[P/J] im fucking going to. i have no other choice
[M/N] and delete these messages. morise might confiscate your phone
[M/N] i just fucking told you another choice
[M/N] what if taking the bracelet off triggers an alarm or a shock
[M/N] if youre with us when you get it off we can have a plasma ally warp us away from morise if needed. if you do it there theyll just kill you
[M/N] youll be vulnerable, possibly unconscious, and in enemy territory
[P/J] malachite its so fucking close to being off and i still cant feel my own fucking hands. star cant warp us, i can
[M/N] if you warp to us we can take care of you
[P/J] ill probably get feeling back in my hands tomorrow. then ill try
[M/N] warp to us and well handle the rest
[P/J] I CANT FEEL MY FUCKING HANDS
[M/N] im reiterating because i want to drive home the point that taking the bracelets off is a terrible idea
[P/J] i. jesus. i just cant think right now
[P/J] malachite im pretty sure im still in shock. lets just talk about this later okay
